posting_body: ['10930 Ashton Avenue', 'Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024', 'Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills', 'Westwood 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Apartment Available This School Year!', 'This 2 bedroom offers the following amenities:', 'Disability Access', 'Central Heat', 'Extra Storage', 'Air Conditioning', 'Mirrored Closet Doors', 'Great Views Available', 'Dishwasher', 'Vertical Blinds', 'Cable Ready', 'Cozy Gas Fireplace', 'Community Amenities:', 'Fitness Center', 'Sauna', 'Controlled Access', 'Roof Terrace', 'BBQ/Grill Area', 'Laundry Facilities', 'Pool', 'Assigned Parking', 'Elevator', 'Westwood two bedroom, two bath apartment with a wide array of stylishly efficient amenities including central air conditioning and heating, large closets, a fireplace, private balcony with fantastic views, kitchen is equipped with a refrigerator, a dishwasher, a microwave, and a gas stove.', 'Nestled just South of Wilshire Blvd., you are in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City.', 'Treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door like Bristol Farms, Sprouts Farmers Market, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s and 99 Ranch Market.', 'Curious about living at Ashton Towers?', 'Book an in-person or virtual tour today with one of our friendly and knowledgeable leasing associates at', 'show contact info', '!', 'Or apply at our website at <URL>', 'Contact: Silton Leasing', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Disclaimer: Pictures are a representation but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Advertised unit availability, rental rates, and terms are updated every 24 hours and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please call for latest availability details.']
